import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['year'] = pd.to_datetime(data['year'], format='%Y', errors='coerce')
    data = data[pd.notna(data['year'])]
    sns.lineplot(x='year', y='wheat', data=data)
    plt.title('What is the trend of wheat production over time?', wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel('Year')
    plt.ylabel('Wheat Production')
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    sns.histplot(data=data, x='wages', color='blue')
    plt.axvline(data['wages'].mean(), color='red', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label='mean')
    plt.axvline(data['wages'].median(), color='green', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label='median')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of wages?', wrap=True)
    plt.legend()
    plt.xlabel('Wages')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['year'] = pd.to_datetime(data['year'], format='%Y', errors='coerce')
    data = data[pd.notna(data['year'])]
    data['year'] = data['year'].dt.strftime('%Y')
    data = data.groupby(['year']).mean().reset_index()
    sns.barplot(x='year', y='wheat', data=data, color='blue', label='Wheat')
    sns.barplot(x='year', y='wages', data=data, color='red', label='Wages')
    plt.legend()
    plt.title('What is the average wheat production and wages over the entire time period?', wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel('Year')
    plt.ylabel('Average')
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
```

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    sns.histplot(data=data, x='wheat', kde=True, color='blue')

    plt.axvline(data['wheat'].median(), color='green', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label=f"Median: {data['wheat'].median():.2f}")
    plt.legend()
    plt.title('What is the distribution of wheat production?')
    plt.xlabel('Wheat Production')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
